v.

and
SAY Service Company, Inc./MAX HVAC and Eastern Waterproofing & Restoration Co., Inc., Defendants. K. Hovnanian at Port Imperial Urban Renewal II, LLC, et al., Defendants/Third-Party Plaintiffs,
v.
RTKL New Jersey Architects, PC, et al., Defendants/Third-Party Defendants. RTKL New Jersey Architects, PA, Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff,
v.
FACE Associates, Inc., Third-Party Defendant. C-45 September Term 2018
081200 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005209-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
